This is the keyboard layout I'm using for [my custom keyboard][].
It's a keyboard with an integrated trackball with 3 keys for the trackball and 35 keys for typing (for 38 keys in total).
The layout is heavily based on the [T-34 keyboard layout][], see the [original T-34 post][] for the background and philosophy of the layout.

