## Mouse layer

Activate using Automatic Mouse Layer: <https://docs.qmk.fm/features/pointing_device>

What should I have on the mouse layer?

- Copy
- Paste
- Left click
- Right click
- Middle click
- Up/dn DPI

- Mods (Shift Ctrl Alt Win), same locations as usual

- Precision/speed modes

